---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Maria's Fav" description="The story behind Maria's Fav and the person picking the products.">
  <article class="page">
    <a href="/" class="back">← Back to the edit</a>

    <header class="page-head">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>Hi, I'm Maria</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        Maria's Fav is my little corner of the internet where I share the products
        I genuinely use and love. I started it because friends kept asking me what
        air fryer I have, which headphones I recommend, and where I got this or
        that — so I decided to put it all in one place.
      </p>
      <p>
        Everything featured here is something I've actually tried. If I wouldn't buy
        it again or recommend it to a friend, it doesn't make the list. No paid
        placements, no products I haven't touched — just honest picks.
      </p>
      <p>
        When you buy through a link on this site, I may earn a small commission as
        an Amazon Associate, at no extra cost to you. That little bit of support is
        what keeps this blog running — thank you. 💛
      </p>
      <p>
        Have a question or a product you think I'd love? I'd be happy to hear from
        you — reach out any time at
        <a href="mailto:mariameira1415@gmail.com">mariameira1415@gmail.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page { max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .back {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .back:hover { color: var(--ink); }
  .page-head { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .eyebrow {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  h1 { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 2.6rem; font-weight: 600; margin: 0; line-height: 1.15; }
  .prose { font-size: 1.08rem; }
  .prose p { margin: 0 0 1.3rem; }
</style>
